<div class="dablink">This article is about the book.  For the term in statistics, see <a href="/wiki/Normal_distribution" title="Normal distribution">normal distribution</a>. For the term in grading, see <a href="/wiki/Bell_curve_grading" title="Bell curve grading">Bell curve grading</a>.</div>
