<td colspan="6">Values are the percentage of each IQ sub-population, among non-Hispanic whites only, fitting each descriptor. Herrnstein &amp; Murray (1994) pp. 171, 158, 163, 174, 230, 180, 132, 194, 247-248, 194, 146 respectively.</td>
