<li id="cite_note-25"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25" title="">^</a></b> slate.com, <a href="http://www.slate.com/id/2128199/" class="external text" title="http://www.slate.com/id/2128199/" rel="nofollow">The Bell Curve Revisited</a>, Stephen Metcalf, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2005-10-17"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="10-17"><a href="/wiki/October_17" title="October 17">October 17</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2005" title="2005">2005</a></span>.</li>
